(This list is based on USGS data and may include former settlements.)

===Adjacent townships===
* [[Driftwood Township, Jackson County, Indiana|Driftwood Township, Jackson County]] (north)
* [[Grassy Fork Township, Jackson County, Indiana|Grassy Fork Township, Jackson County]] (northeast)
* [[Gibson Township, Washington County, Indiana|Gibson Township]] (east)
* [[Washington Township, Washington County, Indiana|Washington Township]] (south)
* [[Jefferson Township, Washington County, Indiana|Jefferson Township]] (west)

===Cemeteries===
The township contains these five cemeteries: Collett, Gater, Peugh, Ridlen and Weston.

